article_title: At least two killed in IDF raid in West Bank.
sentence: At  least  two  Palestinians  died  this  morning  during  Israeli  raids  in  the  West  Bank,  the  Palestinian  Red  Crescent  told  the  AFP  news  agency.

article_title: At least two killed in IDF raid in West Bank.
sentence: A  45-year-old  man  was  killed  in  Jenin  and  another  person  died  in  Dheisheh  refugee  camp,  the  report  said.
